data.description: Embrace waterfront living in this captivating property nestled along a serene canal leading to the picturesque Fowl River. Boasting a bulkheaded expanse and a private boat slip, this home offers the ultimate coastal lifestyle. Tucked away at the end of a short gravel road that culminates in a quiet cul-de-sac, privacy and tranquility are the hallmarks of this location. Home is on pilings, therefore there is an entire outside living space for entertaining.     Featuring 2 bedrooms and 2 baths, this residence goes beyond the ordinary with an additional office space that has served as a nursery, catering to the diverse needs of modern living. The primary bedroom stands out with its dual closets, providing ample storage for your wardrobe and personal belongings.    The kitchen, a focal point of this home, is equipped with a gas stove (connected to Spire gas supply) and a convenient wall oven. Functionality meets style in this space, making it a delightful hub for culinary endeavors. For added convenience, a generator is currently in working order and can remain, though its continued functionality is not warranted.    Step into an open-concept living area that seamlessly connects various spaces, creating an inviting atmosphere for both relaxation and entertainment. The rooms throughout are generously proportioned, ensuring comfort and versatility in daily living.    This residence has been thoughtfully updated to enhance both form and function. Recent improvements include a 2021 HVAC system, updated ductwork, and a smart thermostat for efficient climate control. Further, the sink and faucet were updated in 2023, ensuring a contemporary and functional kitchen space. The water heater was replaced in 2021, adding to the overall efficiency and comfort of the home. The flooring was tastefully upgraded in 2012, and a new roof was installed in 2015, providing peace of mind for years to come.    Experience the perfect blend of modern updates and timeless functionality in this waterfront haven. With its idyllic location, spacious layout, and thoughtful upgrades, this property invites you to embark on a new chapter of coastal living. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional residence your own – schedule a showing today.      Updates include: roof=2015; Hot water heater=2021; Flooring=2012; HVAC & Ductwork=2021. Inside painted including scraping & painting the ceilings and light fixtures over the years. ***Listing Broker makes no representation to accuracy of square footage. Buyer to verify. Any/All updates per seller(s).***
